1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,320
I'm fine, somehow I'm fine.

2
00:00:02,320 --> 00:00:06,520
I uncovered myself and despite the lights being on, nothing was in the house.

3
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:08,760
I've searched every room and nothing.

4
00:00:08,760 --> 00:00:11,440
I'm sitting now in the corner of my bedroom.

5
00:00:11,440 --> 00:00:13,400
My wife still lies in our bed.

6
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,960
I tried moving her, but I got frightened.

7
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:18,880
I was afraid I'd break something by accident.

8
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:22,520
Although I've noticed that the rot and rigour have accelerated at a faster rate than they

9
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:26,840
should, it's like time is going faster than I can comprehend it.

10
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:30,520
I'm watching my wife with her away faster than my grief for her.

11
00:00:30,520 --> 00:00:33,160
I hope she knows in heaven that I'm still here.

12
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:36,520
I've been in darkness so long that I've forgotten what day it is.
